---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const baseUrl = base || '/';
const docsUrl = `${baseUrl}getting-started/introduction`;
---

<LandingLayout title="凌霄剑域 · LingXiao">
  <!-- === Hero === -->
  <section class="lx-hero">
    <div class="lx-hero-content">
      <img src={`${baseUrl}logo.svg`} alt="凌霄 Logo" class="lx-hero-logo" />
      <div class="lx-hero-badge">AI Engineering Orchestration Kernel</div>
      <h1>凌霄剑域</h1>
      <p class="lx-hero-tagline">
        给 AI 一个工程内核，而不只是一个对话框。<br/>
        <span class="lx-accent">专家团</span>协同、<span class="lx-accent">任务 DAG</span>编排、<span class="lx-accent">全状态同步</span>——<br/>
        让复杂工程<span class="lx-gold">可调度、可审查、可恢复</span>。
      </p>
      <div class="lx-install-cmd">
        <code>git clone https://github.com/hexian2001/lingxiao.git && npm install && npm run build && npm link</code>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-hero-cta">
        <a href={docsUrl} class="lx-btn lx-btn-primary">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"/></svg>
          快速上手
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/hexian2001/lingxiao" class="lx-btn lx-btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          源码仓库
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- === 核心特性 === -->
  <section class="lx-features">
    <h2 class="lx-section-title">为什么不是另一个聊天壳</h2>
    <p class="lx-section-subtitle">六层工程能力，把"和模型对话"变成"指挥一个工程团队"</p>
    <div class="lx-feature-grid">
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>专家团，不是独白</h3>
        <p>Leader 理解目标、拆任务、建 DAG、调度专家；Worker 各司其职——架构、后端、前端、研究、QA、审查。13 种预设角色，每个 Worker 有独立上下文和工具链。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="12" r="3"/><line x1="6" y1="9" x2="6" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="6" x2="15" y2="11"/><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="13"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>DAG 让复杂可调度</h3>
        <p>目标自动拆解为带依赖的任务图。无依赖的并行跑，有依赖的按序解锁。每个任务有 owner、状态、阻塞关系、结果回执——不是一串线性对话。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>三端同一份状态</h3>
        <p>WebUI、TUI、CLI 不各自猜状态。SSE + ACP JSON-RPC 把 session、leader、worker、task、permission 统一到一个运行态快照，流式事件负责体验，快照负责校准。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>真实工具，不是嘴上说说</h3>
        <p>100+ 内置工具在权限系统下运行：文件读写、Shell、Git、浏览器自动化、Office/PDF、Workflow 画布、MCP 统一入口。Agent 的每一步都有日志和证据。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>验收闭环，不是"说完成就完成"</h3>
        <p>每个任务完成时触发结构化验收：PASS/FAIL/BLOCKED。投机执行跑多分支择优，对抗验证做退出码断言，契约五阶段闭环——contract → implement → evaluate → repair → reset。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-feature-card">
        <div class="lx-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>MCP Forge + Skills</h3>
        <p>模板驱动生成 MCP Server：需求 → 模板 → 生成 → 沙箱 → Inspector → 注册。Skills 四层优先级自动注入 Worker 上下文。不是插件市场摆设，是运行时能力。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- === 功能展示 === -->
  <section class="lx-showcase">
    <div class="lx-showcase-grid">
      <div class="lx-showcase-image">
        <img src={`${baseUrl}screenshots/chat.png`} alt="凌霄 WebUI 指挥中心" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="lx-showcase-text">
        <h3>指挥中心，不是聊天窗口</h3>
        <p>任务 DAG 实时可视化、Agent 面板、工具调用全链路追踪、审查证据、Git 工作台、黑板图谱、浏览器终端——像指挥一个工程团队一样指挥 AI。</p>
        <ul>
          <li>任务 DAG 实时可视化与依赖追踪</li>
          <li>Agent 面板：角色、运行态、任务绑定</li>
          <li>工具调用全链路日志与证据采集</li>
          <li>审查证据与验收报告</li>
          <li>设计市场、插件管理与 MCP 配置</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- === 架构图 === -->
  <section class="lx-architecture">
    <h2 class="lx-section-title">架构概览</h2>
    <p class="lx-section-subtitle">Leader-Worker 编排内核 + 全状态同步链路</p>
    <div class="lx-arch-diagram">
      <pre>{`User ──→ TUI / CLI ──→ SessionManager ──→ SessionRuntime ──→ LeaderAgent
                                                                    │
                                     ┌──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────┐
                                     ▼                              ▼                  ▼
                               TaskBoard / DAG              AgentPool           ToolRegistry
                                     │                      │                     │
                                     ▼                      ▼                     ▼
                              Worker Experts ←────────── Pool ←─────────── Git / Workbench
                                     │
                                     ▼
                                SQLite DB

User ──→ WebUI ──→ ACP JSON-RPC + SSE ──→ SessionManager (同上链路)`}</pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- === 对比表 === -->
  <section class="lx-comparison">
    <h2 class="lx-section-title">凌霄 vs 普通 AI 编码工具</h2>
    <p class="lx-section-subtitle">差别不在"能不能写代码"，而在"能不能工程化"</p>
    <table class="lx-comparison-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>普通 AI 编码工具</th>
          <th class="lx-highlight">凌霄剑域</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>架构</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">单 Agent 线性对话</td>
          <td class="lx-check">Leader + Worker 专家团</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>任务编排</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">一问一答，无依赖管理</td>
          <td class="lx-check">DAG 依赖图 + 并行执行</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>状态同步</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">单端运行，无跨端同步</td>
          <td class="lx-check">WebUI / TUI / CLI 三端实时</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>验收</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">模型说完成即完成</td>
          <td class="lx-check">契约循环 + 对抗验证</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>工具</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">内置固定工具集</td>
          <td class="lx-check">100+ 工具 + MCP Forge</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>可恢复性</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">会话丢失不可恢复</td>
          <td class="lx-check">SQLite 持久化 + 会话恢复</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>自治</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">无自治能力</td>
          <td class="lx-check">Eternal 巡逻 + 自动重启</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>LLM 网关</td>
          <td class="lx-cross">依赖外部 API</td>
          <td class="lx-check">本地 Gateway + 虚拟密钥</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <!-- === Footer === -->
  <footer class="lx-footer">
    <div class="lx-footer-content">
      <div class="lx-footer-brand">
        <img src={`${baseUrl}logo.svg`} alt="凌霄" />
        <span>凌霄剑域 LingXiao v0.3.9</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-footer-links">
        <a href={docsUrl}>文档</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/hexian2001/lingxiao" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}reference/changelog`}>更新日志</a>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}reference/faq`}>FAQ</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/hexian2001/lingxiao/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">问题反馈</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lx-footer-copy">
        © 2025 LingXiao. AGPL-3.0 License.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</LandingLayout>
